insert into JournalArticle (articleId, version, portletId, groupId, companyId, userId, userName, createDate, modifiedDate, title, content, type_, structureId, templateId, displayDate, approved, approvedByUserId, approvedByUserName) values ('COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES', 1.0, '15', '3', 'liferay.com', 'liferay.com.1', 'John Wayne', now(), now(), 'Company Case Studies', '<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n\n<root>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"main-text\" type=\"text_area\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[<DIV>Liferay is dedicated to providing enterprise solutions for firms across all industries - from small to large sized business. Liferay delivers a high quality software without the high cost that comes with licensed software. Unlike other open source software that comes without support, you can expect our staff and community to support our software around the clock. Read about which companies around the world are choosing <U>Liferay</U>.</DIV>]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-name-1\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[3sixteen]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-url-1\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[www.3sixteen.com]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-summary-1\" type=\"text_box\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[3sixteen has always had an eye out for movements in music and culture and has not been bashful in perpetuating positive statements with cutting-edge and intelligent design work. 3sixteen clothing is carried in some of the most cutting edge boutiques in New York, Chicago, LA, San Francisco, Australia, Japan and other locations across the world.]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-logo-1\" type=\"image\">\n    <dynamic-content>/image/journal/article?img_id=COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES.study-logo-1&amp;version=1.0</dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-details-url-1\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://@cms_url@/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-3SIXTEEN]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-name-2\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[Bangkok Airways]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-url-2\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[www.bangkokair.com]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-summary-2\" type=\"text_box\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[With over thirty-six years of operations, Bangkok Airways has maintained not only highly efficient operations and first class service but also ensured that safety is a major priority. The company has obtained permits to operate scheduled flights in 20 major routes, covering nearly all-major resort destinations of Thailand. In addition, the company has also obtained the right to fly internationally to Siem Reap, Phnom-Penh; the capital of Cambodia, Jinghong; the capital of Xishuangbanna region, Xi\'An and Guilin in China, Luang Prabang in Laos and Singapore.]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-logo-2\" type=\"image\">\n    <dynamic-content>/image/journal/article?img_id=COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES.study-logo-2&amp;version=1.0</dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-details-url-2\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://@cms_url@/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-BANGKOK-AIRWAYS]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-name-3\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[BT Group]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-url-3\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[www.bt.com]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-summary-3\" type=\"text_box\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[BT Group is one of Europe\'s leading providers of telecommunications services. Its principal activities include local, national and international telecommunications services, higher-value broadband and internet products and services, and IT solutions. In the UK, BT serves over 20 million business and residential customers with more than 29 million exchange lines, as well as providing network services to other licensed operators.]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-logo-3\" type=\"image\">\n    <dynamic-content>/image/journal/article?img_id=COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES.study-logo-3&amp;version=1.0</dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-details-url-3\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-name-4\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[EducaMadrid]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-url-4\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[www.educa.madrid.org]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-summary-4\" type=\"text_box\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[EducaMadrid represents the Madrid, Spain school system which accounts for over 500,000 students across 1,600 schools.]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-logo-4\" type=\"image\">\n    <dynamic-content>/image/journal/article?img_id=COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES.study-logo-4&amp;version=1.0</dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-details-url-4\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://@cms_url@/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-EDUCAMADRID]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-name-5\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[Jason\'s Deli]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-url-5\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[www.jasonsdeli.com]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-summary-5\" type=\"text_box\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[Jason\'s Deli is a deli that boasts 135+ stores. Jason\'s Deli Restaurants (mainly in Texas) sell a total of more than 100 items, from salad bar to big, Texas-sized sandwiches.]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-logo-5\" type=\"image\">\n    <dynamic-content>/image/journal/article?img_id=COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES.study-logo-5&amp;version=1.0</dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-details-url-5\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://@cms_url@/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-JASONS-DELI]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-name-6\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[Oakwood Worldwide]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-url-6\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[www.oakwood.com]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-summary-6\" type=\"text_box\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[Oakwood Worldwide is the largest temporary housing provider worldwide. With 40 years of multi-family housing experience, and 30 years of industry leadership in corporate housing, Oakwood Worldwide is the most experienced leader in temporary furnished apartments. With access to over 400,000 apartments in more than 2,000 U.S. cities, as well as select locations in Canada, Asia, and Europe, 85% of Fortune 500 firms depend on Oakwood Worldwide.]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-logo-6\" type=\"image\">\n    <dynamic-content>/image/journal/article?img_id=COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES.study-logo-6&amp;version=1.0</dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"study-details-url-6\" type=\"text\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[http://@cms_url@/COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-OAKWOOD]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n</root>', 'general', 'COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES', 'COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES', now(), 'true', 'liferay.com.1', 'John Wayne');
insert into JournalArticle (articleId, version, portletId, groupId, companyId, userId, userName, createDate, modifiedDate, title, content, type_, structureId, templateId, displayDate, approved, approvedByUserId, approvedByUserName) values ('COMPANY-CASE-STUDIES-3SIXTEEN', 1.0, '15', '3', 'liferay.com', 'liferay.com.1', 'John Wayne', now(), now(), 'Company Case Studies 3sixteen', '<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n\n<root>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"main-text\" type=\"text_area\">\n    <dynamic-content><![CDATA[<DIV>\"<I>3sixteen needed an e-commerce solution that was flexible enough to grow with us over time, and yet was quick and easy to get running. We knew that our front end website was visually appealing enough to attract customers, but we wanted a separate site to integrate with that would serve as the purchasing solution. We also wanted a system that would integrate easily with PayPal. The Liferay portal system has met all these needs and more - today, we use it for our online store, our email system, and our document manager.</I>\" - Andrew Chen, Partner - 3sixteen <BR><BR><B>Company Profile</B><BR><BR>As the urban streetwear market continues to mature, it is clear that apparel consumers are starting to look for substance within clothing. Although mass branding will continue to hold its place within the arena, a growing interest in apparel that has a voice and holds a message has become apparent. 3sixteen fabrications, an up and coming streetwear line out of New York City, has a vision to influence the market by providing messages and social commentary through fashion. Since its inception in the Spring of 2003, 3sixteen has always had an eye out for movements in music and culture and has not been bashful in perpetuating positive statements with cutting-edge and intelligent design work. 3sixteen clothing is carried in some of the most cutting edge boutiques in New York, Chicago, LA, San Francisco, Australia, Japan and other locations across the world. <BR><BR><B>Challenge</B><BR><BR>In an industry like fashion which relies on cutting-edge appearance and presentation, 3sixteen needed to keep its Flash MX front-end website that would serve as the \"brochure\" site which would not be used to sell clothing, but rather an experience through the music, graphics, and articles. Due to the static nature of Flash, however, it would not make sense to use the brochure site as the e-commerce solution since products would need to be added, removed and updated on a constant basis throughout each season. 3sixteen therefore needed a back-end system that would allow customers to create personal accounts (thereby eliminating the need for return customers to keep entering the same shipping and contact information each time), place orders, and track order statuses. From the business side, 3sixteen also needed a system that could send automated status emails to customers, compile a purchase order tracking list, and collect customer funds through Paypal. <BR><BR><B>Resolution</B><BR><BR>The Liferay team came through for 3sixteen with a customized solution that met all of its needs. Aesthetics were secondary, since the company already had the brochure site to sell the \"image\" - the portal system was built for functionality. The live 3sixteen e-commerce solution offers: \n<UL>\n<LI>Personalized customer logins and accounts. \n<LI>Easy product management that allows extensive descriptions, image uploading, category and SKU organization and more without any coding knowledge. \n<LI>Real-time payment integration with PayPal. \n<LI>Printable purchase orders. \n<LI>System-generated order and shipping confirmation emails. \n<LI>Notes fields which mark each comment with the author and the time/date it was entered. \n<LI>Document management. \n<LI>Mailing list integration.</LI></UL></DIV>]]></dynamic-content>\n  </dynamic-element>\n  <dynamic-element name=\"screenshot-thumbnail-1\" type=\"image\">\n    <dynamic-content>http://www.liferay.com/static/image/COMPAN